title: 66 Portland Place Building Tour
desc: 66 Portland Place Building Tours For a discounted price during the Palladian season, join us for a tour of our unique building full of beautiful Art Deco inspired details, interesting architectural history and hidden stories.  Tours take fortnightly every Saturday from 10 October to 19 December. *A limited number of tickets will be available on the door on a first come, first served basis. ?You can pay the tour guide prior to the start of the tour (cash only).
